    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays absolutely flawless inside and out. It\u2019s super clean, still has that fresh car feel, and honestly, you won't find another one this pristine on the market. I'm sad to let it go, but I'd love for it to find a home with someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
