      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless original paint and deep, mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every electronic component functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full service history and a drive that is tight, responsive, and completely free of any rattles or imperfections. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a pristine example of automotive excellence.",
